author: Hayalperest
text:
A small gym, but well-equipped with everything you need for a solid workout!

All my favourite machines are here, including the preacher curl bench and the cable crossover machine.

The staff are humble and friendly not rude or snobbish like in some other places. Even during peak hours the gym is not crowded which makes for a comfortable workout environment.

This was my first time at this branch, and I must say it didn‚Äôt disappoint.

text: It's a new outlet near to where I lived. Equipment are comparable to those higher-end gym chains although lacks in number. Not as big as AF Northpoint or Sembawang shopping centre, but it's decent. There's squat racks and space for deadlifts (although no platform). Overall would foresee myself visiting here to train often.
